### Test Push Notification Service Status
GET http://localhost:8082/api/push-notifications/status
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Test Regular Push Notification
POST http://localhost:8082/api/push-notifications/test
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pushToken": "{{fcm_token}}",
  "deviceType": "android"
}

### Test FCM Push Notification (Debug)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/push-notifications/test-fcm
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pushToken": "{{fcm_token}}",
  "deviceType": "android"
}

### Register Push Token
POST http://localhost:8082/api/push-notifications/register
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pushToken": "{{fcm_token}}",
  "deviceType": "android"
}

### Get User's Push Tokens
GET http://localhost:8082/api/push-notifications/tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

